{"tid":37352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣爛路奇蹟！　正妹新車車牌震到噴飛","createTime":"2016-12-13T09:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T12:10:49.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84b2717c3492ad49dbbcb0448f299713cd039066","tid":37352,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:45:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20161213/1010732/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%88%9B%E8%B7%AF%E5%A5%87%E8%B9%9F%EF%BC%81%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E6%96%B0%E8%BB%8A%E8%BB%8A%E7%89%8C%E9%9C%87%E5%88%B0%E5%99%B4%E9%A3%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Flife%2F20161213%2F1010732%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%2588%259B%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%25B9%259F%25EF%25BC%2581%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25BB%258A%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%2589%258C%25E9%259C%2587%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%2599%25B4%25E9%25A3%259B&d=YkKN8ErseoKdUdwvRorTiHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=39263978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/life/20161213/1010732/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%88%9B%E8%B7%AF%E5%A5%87%E8%B9%9F%EF%BC%81%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E6%96%B0%E8%BB%8A%E8%BB%8A%E7%89%8C%E9%9C%87%E5%88%B0%E5%99%B4%E9%A3%9B</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161213/640_4f967587f1952eda9796cebf4447cdd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161213%2F640_4f967587f1952eda9796cebf4447cdd6.jpg&h=e7b8cf80&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n2016年12月13日00:00 <br />\n台灣路爛到可以震斷車牌！一名正妹女大生前天在《臉書》不公開社團「爆怨公社」發文，表示騎著才買半年的新機車行經台中市文心路時，竟然因為爛路震震震而把車牌震到斷掉飛出去，「藍瘦香菇又森氣」。 <br />\n<br />\n瑄兒對《蘋果》表示，當天是男友騎車載她從彰化到台中玩，行經文心路時，本來還自覺像超級瑪莉歐，遇到窟窿會跳起來，想不到男友突然從照後鏡看到有白白的東西飛出去，「結果我一個轉頭我的車牌竟然不見了！而且飛超級無敵遠，我超傻眼，我們趕快回頭回去撿」。 <br />\n<br />\n之後的行程，瑄兒表示，她就一路舉著車牌，同行的同學一直笑，連路人也一直笑，「我覺得自己好可憐」。而這塊見證台灣爛路的車牌，最後被瑄兒載去修理，花了一千多元，現在雖然修好了，但很擔心又會再斷，她感嘆，「文心路真的...可以上演實體瑪莉歐遊戲...」，而且「很多網友說many擋泥板超脆弱」。 <br />\n<br />\n其他網友們則是紛紛留言，「Many的通病」、「中清跟文心路根本就是越野啊」、「哈哈哈哈神扯」、「樓主表情無奈」、「我也騎Many，車牌擋泥板也斷了2次」、「因為路不平而掉的我第一次聽到欸XD」、「其實臺灣到哪路都爛啦」。（劉育良／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"f071ded9d64e4f19b6d8c925ea815122d3a47ccc","tid":37352,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:46:53.000Z","msg":"馬總統看手錶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d7664f80eb89cc52660cfc87d1118d66eb3ac1","tid":37352,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T09:48:49.000Z","msg":"以潮噴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd9e9fb9794288cd05538f578d43c1812f4c49b7","tid":37352,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"處女膜都已經唔存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怕咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c444f1587f632e0100efcafd9ed5ef307c105836","tid":37352,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:06:54.000Z","msg":"正妹車震噴飛"},{"pid":"6375544a39bcf8583d5f6108d88455a92272ce62","tid":37352,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:09:03.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n成撚日渣呢條路<br />\n爛撚到喊"},{"pid":"24bce596296209f60d9b4d12d95bb1367b948e51","tid":37352,"uid":54278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<br />\n成撚日渣呢條路<br />\n爛撚到喊</blockquote><br />\n屌你呀  台中做野定讀書"},{"pid":"d36dc99fd519a7041d79a94c2d165f18f4de67dd","tid":37352,"uid":10466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"屌，彰化尐路用半年就壞"},{"pid":"d35cfe296191b8bdd640d23910ae02b5aaad7787","tid":37352,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T12:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌<br />\n成撚日渣呢條路<br />\n爛撚到喊</blockquote><br />\n屌你呀  台中做野定讀書</blockquote><br />